REpower Quarterly Profit Doubles; Company Confirms Forecast

-- B y   M a r i a j o s e   V e r a
-- 
2011-08-12T07:15:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-12/repower-quarterly-profit-doubles-company-confirms-forecast.html
REpower Systems Group said net
income rose to 4.2 million euros in the first quarter from 1.8
million euros in the year-ago period. Incoming orders fell to
218 million euros. The company confirmed its forecast for
“significant sales and earnings growth” in the 2011/2012
fiscal year.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mariajose Vera at 
 mvera1@bloomberg.net  